Package qemujuicy

QemuJuicy - GUI for QEMU virtual machines management.
Author:
Heinz Silberbauer
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppProperties
    Application properties.
    Check
    Helper class for development checks (similar to "assert").
    CommandLineArgs
    Command line parser and option container for the program.
    Files
    Files and directories utility and container, implemented as a singleton.
    Help
    Help handler.
    Images
    Container for all application images.
    Logger
    Logger, a simple logging utility, could be a wrapper for java.util.Logger or log4j, you may be change to it in the future, of course.
    Main
    QEMU Juicy - VM emulator GUI (main entry), QEMU Java User Interface Contributed Yet.
    Msg
    Msg (short for Message): a utility to provide strings/messages for other languages.
    Parser
    Simple parser for parsing text files.
    ProcessExecutor
    Executor of a process.
    QemuSetup
    QEMU setup of the application, looking for a valid QEMU installation.
    Usage
    Prints a usage of this program.
    Util
    Utility class, supporting the project with several static methods and constants.
    Version
    Version information of the project.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Message
    Uses hard coded messages as Enumeration, other languages could be added later, import this as static for convenience.
    OSType
    Operating system utility (for different operating systems and their behaviour).
